name: Spring Roll Wrappers
author: PATTY5
summary: This is a simple recipe for preparing homemade flour spring roll wrappers. Be sure to plan ahead, as the dough needs to chill several hours or overnight.
directions: Sift bread flour into a medium bowl and make a well in the center
Place egg and cold water in well
Beat with a wooden spoon until a smooth dough has formed
Cover with plastic wrap and chill in the refrigerator 4 hours, or overnight
On a lightly floured surface, roll the dough into an approximately 14x14 inch square
Roll each square into a very thin 6x6 inch square
Cover with plastic wrap and refrigerate until ready to use
